Former Johannesburg Mayor, Mpho Moerane, has passed away on Wednesday. Courtesy of #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG - Former Johannesburg mayor Mpho Moerane has died. He succumbed to injuries sustained in a car accident last week. READ: Moerane in critical condition after car crash He leaves behind his wife, four children and other family members. The family has asked for privacy to mourn his death.